snippet.title: Amar Akbhar Anthoni (Amar Akbar Anthony) 2019 New Hindi Dubbed Full Movie | Ravi Teja, Ileana
snippet.description:
A man suffering from Dissociative Identity Disorder has to take revenge against four businessmen for the murder of his family while his past confronts him in the form of his childhood love.

Movie:- Amar Akbhar Anthoni (Amar Akbar Anthony)
Starcast:- Ravi Teja, Ileana D'Cruz, Vikramjeet Virk, Abhimanyu Singh, Sunil, Sayaji Shinde, Raghu Babu, Vennela Kishore, Jaya Prakash Reddy, Srinivasa Reddy.
Music by:- S. S. Thaman
Produced by: Manish Shah
Directed by: Srinu Vaitla
